title: Dolphins & Whales Relax With Nature Vol. 7
description:
DOLPHINS & WHALES Relax with Nature Vol. 7

An underwater world of magical intensity. Dolphins' gentle playful voices seem to speak directly to the soul, awakening a realisation of kinship and love. The deep resonance of Whalesong wraps the senses in an emotive cocoon of pure communion.

"If you love it enough, anything will talk to you." George Washington Carver
